{"tid":2093933,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德國柏林地鐵站名被指種族歧視黑人 有要要求改為非裔男子弗洛伊德　交通局決定以俄羅斯國歌作者改名","createTime":"2020-07-04T07:56:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T10:17:02.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5270bbe7be4d24bfb28d448d4c467dde47d431bd","tid":2093933,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T07:56:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/493814/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%9F%8F%E6%9E%97%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%90%8D%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B1%80%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F493814%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259F%258F%25E6%259E%2597%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%25BC%2595%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E6%2597%258F%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2580%259A%25E5%25B1%2580%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2590%258D&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2IKb0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=a4ecfb34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/493814/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%9F%8F%E6%9E%97%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E7%AB%99%E5%90%8D%E5%BC%95%E8%B5%B7%E7%A8%AE%E6%97%8F%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BA%A4%E9%80%9A%E5%B1%80%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%94%B9%E5%90%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n美國非裔男子弗洛伊德（George Floyd）之死，全球多個地方因而發起黑人平權活動。在德國首都柏林，當地一個地鐵站名因為帶有貶低黑人之意，當局決定為它另改名字。<br />\n<br />\n柏林公共交通公司（BVG）7月3日宣布，由於就街名出現爭議，位於地標勃蘭登堡門（Brandenburg Gate）附近的默倫街車站（Mohrenstrasse）會改名為格林卡街車站（Glinkastrasse），並強調當局向任何形式的種族主義和歧視說不。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n默倫（Mohr）在古代德語的意思為黑人，同時亦有「蠢人」之意。該條街道在1707年命名，有歷史研究指街道名字是與普魯士親王菲利普&middot;威廉（Philipp Wilhelm von Brandenburg-Schwedt）獲得的黑奴有關。弗洛伊德死後，有德國示威者將默倫街車站改名為「弗洛伊德街車站」（George Floyd strasse）。<br />\n<br />\n柏林交通部門決定為默倫街車站改名，平息種族歧視爭議。（Reuters）<br />\n柏林交通部門決定為默倫街車站改名，平息種族歧視爭議。（Reuters）<br />\n<br />\n默倫街車站是柏林地鐵2號線的其中一個車站，在1908年啟用，期間曾經過多次改名，直到1991年東西德統一後採用現有名字。而新名字的格林卡（Glinka）則是源於19世紀俄羅斯作曲家米哈伊爾&middot;伊萬諾維奇&middot;格林卡（Mikhail Ivanovich Glinka，又譯葛令卡），俄羅斯舊國歌《愛國歌》（Patriotic Song）就是出自他的手筆。"},{"pid":"27079478c334d63e22951f3b650af69548bb6643","tid":2093933,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T07:58:29.000Z","msg":"冇嘢搵嘢嚟搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1be64043069d5c0205559333717c33fb437db9","tid":2093933,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T08:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3412403a1a598fe0d25c14374d91afcdb14ecd5a","tid":2093933,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c094268dbc517cf228c2d933158e97828ff0dc","tid":2093933,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:24:50.000Z","msg":"搵個慣犯個名做街名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826d8feeaf54eb1eb55603daa11abeb30576baf3","tid":2093933,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"戇鳩無極限，"},{"pid":"0a6ac1f3ffaad646e578b82666de51ee3be1a451","tid":2093933,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T09:41:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔改BLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2366384755c91a9d5bc72c8f279ab50cbd672109","tid":2093933,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T10:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3KfmK5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3KfmK5D.jpg&h=2b495cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CBAPxg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn